VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT xml\.etree\.ElementTree\.parse\s*\(|ElementTree\.parse\s*\(|xml\.dom\.minidom\.parse\s*\(|xml\.sax\.parse\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:defusedxml|no_network|resolve_entities\s*=\s*False
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects standard library XML parsers known to be vulnerable to XXE when parsing untrusted input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for XXE: stdlib xml.etree.ElementTree Vulnerable Parser.
